  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there were so many people [INAUDIBLE] from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were from the bunkers, from-- from-- from the basements, and from all over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were running, like-- like flies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we want to kill off [INAUDIBLE] flies is flying away from you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the strength wasn't-- wasn't any stronger than the flies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But passing by, the same my sister's house, as I said.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I indicated that, you know, there was so close by.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I-- we-- I couldn't go through the front.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The-- the doors from the back entrance as-- where his cow were, where his horse was, was, like, opened.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Come in, Molly, like somebody would call me, come in, Molly, hide yourself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Here I-- I never even was dreaming to be there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I never saw how it looks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So there was wood, cutted woods, and on the woods were sacks, bags, large bags, where you will have the grain in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But a few of them, two or three, were laying like this, empty, on the wood.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So then I, so I walked in, and I closed the door very, very hardly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was like a steel-- steel stick, and I closed it from the inside.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But they probably noticed me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I managed to crawl, to see what there were also non-cutted wood.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I remembered that my sister told me that there will be a barrel with-- with flour, in case winter, if we will be living so I should know that there is flour.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I [INAUDIBLE] I-- I pulled away the one or two from those non-cutted woods, and here I noticed, thought to myself, this is a place where I can hide myself.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Maybe this will help me.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
